ATM Deposit

INPUT
-Account number
-PIN

Process
-Prompt user for account number
-validate the account number
-Save the account number in variable
-Prompt user for PIN
-Validate the PIN
-Save the PIN in variable
-Prompt user to deposit
-Add money to the current balance
- Add Current balance and deposited amount
-Put new balance in total
-Print total

Out Put
-Total

----------------------------------

ATM Withdraws
INPUT
-Account number
-PIN

Process
-Prompt user for account number
-validate the account number
-Save the account number in variable
-Prompt user for PIN
-Validate the PIN
-Save the PIN in variable
-Prompt user for withdrawal amount
-Subtract from the available balance if the available balance is not zero
-Put new balance minus available balance in remaining balance
-Print remaining balance

Out Put
- Remaining balance

----------------------------------

Checking Balance
Input
-Account number
-PIN

Process
-Prompt user for account number
-Validate account number
-Save account number in variable
-Prompt user for PIN
-Validate PIN number
-Save PIN in variable
-Give option for the user to choose for remaining balance
-Print remaining balance

